 ## FAQ
 
-**How are AI product docs different from ordinary API docs?**
+**Do AI products still need traditional technical writing, or can prompt design replace it?**
 
-AI docs need to explain variability and evaluation, not just syntax. A normal API doc can stop at request shape, auth, and response fields. An AI doc also needs tested scope, known limits, model or prompt assumptions, and whatever tool or retrieval context affects the result.
